  <prompt>
    Implement the upload finalization worker that takes temporary file uploads,
    moves them to permanent SPE storage, creates Document records, and updates
    job status. Handle EmailArtifact creation for email saves.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    .NET developer specializing in file processing. Expert in SharePoint Embedded,
    document management, and error handling.
  </role>

  <goal>
    A reliable upload worker that finalizes document saves by moving files to SPE
    and creating all necessary records.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      When a user submits a save request, files are initially stored temporarily.
      The upload worker finalizes the save by moving files to permanent SPE storage,
      creating Document records with proper associations, and EmailArtifact/AttachmentArtifact
      for email saves.
    </background>
